PicMe INSTALL


Simple installation instructions.  
If you run into problems, send me an email.


Simple installation instructions:

1. Rename settings.php.dev in the root directory to settings.php.  Edit as needed.
2. Upload all files to your server.
3. Make the picuploads directory writable.  example: chmod 777 members
4. Execute install.php, located in the admin folder.
5. Delete all install.php file in the admin directory.
6. Go to admin: http://www.YOURSITE.COM/admin/ to login.


Good Luck,
Have fun,
and Behave!

